Biographic film about Russian scientist, one of the creators of radio, Aleksandr Popov. Although the storyline of the film was influenced by the ideological situation in the post-war Soviet Union, this is a good specimen of numerous biopics of the 1940s Soviet cinema. Internal subtitles en Esperanto.

